Build and Install:
=================
1) Set the following Variables in Makefile
	a) GSDK_ROOT = /path/to/graphics SDK root
        b) TGTFS_PATH = /path/to/NFS/Flesystem
	c) CROSS_COMPILE= CROSS_COMPILE_PREFIX

Run the following to build install the binary on to the NULL WINDOW SYSTEM platform -

-  make && make install

Run the following to build and install the binary on to the X-WINDOW SYSTEM platform -

-  make XORG_BUILD=1 && make install
 
Note:- You need to put on Red-Cyan glasses to have 3D effect
